sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant App as Android App
    participant Firestore
    participant CF as Cloud Function<br/>onEmergencyAlert
    participant FCM
    participant Guardian

    User->>App: Tap panic button
    App->>Firestore: Create alert doc (PANIC, userId, location)
    Firestore->>CF: onCreate trigger
    CF->>Firestore: Read users/{userId} → guardians[]
    loop For each guardian
        CF->>Firestore: Read users/{guardianId}.fcmToken
        CF->>FCM: Send notification
        FCM->>Guardian: Push (Emergency Alert)
    end
    CF->>Firestore: Write alert_logs